    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Tachydromia punctifera (Becker) (Canada, Northwest Territories; CNC). A–E. Male. A. Habitus, lateral view. B. Head, anterior view. C. Hypopygium, dorsal view. D. Right surstylus, lateral view. E. Left epandrial lamella and left surstylus, lateral view. F. Female head, anterior view. Abbreviations: cerc—cercus; lft sur—left surstylus; rt sur—right surstylus. C–E: scale bar is 0.1 mm." ;
